...and he was hiding it from me.

721
01:10:31,480 --> 01:10:33,311
And I thought that...

722
01:10:34,160 --> 01:10:35,798
...might be a possible reason...

723
01:10:36,480 --> 01:10:37,754
...a possible reason for him to...

724
01:10:38,040 --> 01:10:39,439
